{
  "stem": "21978.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they didn't discuss it-- didn't discuss it with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we knew that the situation is very grave, because of the economic situation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The parents lost their jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My mother had to do some sewing at home to earn living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What we earned in the-- in the orphanage, we have supplied them with some help.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I know that we were always sorry we can't do much more for them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But my father was hawking some soap maybe or, you know-- from house to house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because he-- nobody would employ him as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We, as young girls, I remember that having this yellow Star of David, we walked once on the street, and we were caught by a Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were forced to go to clean floors in a villa in some better-- better part of the town, which was taken away from Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And German were taking over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we had to clean the floors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We didn't know how to clean parquet floors, I know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I remember that one of the German soldiers even showed us how to do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because we didn't know how to clean floors and polish it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we had to-- if in-- we-- we hadn't been not able to go not only to cinema and theaters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And parks were forbidden to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were not allowed to sit in the tram in the same carriage, as the first carriage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had only the second carriage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "On the-- there were some-- some streets which were not for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the center of the city shopping-- the-- shoppings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They are done at the different times for Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
